Program: Great Lives
Title: Richard Beckinsale
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00gj68j
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 9 Jan 2007
Actor and comedian Alan Davies nominates Richard Beckinsale, the actor whose life was so brief that no one has yet written it up. With contributions from Stephen Frears, who directed him in two films, and from Richard Beckinsale's widow Judy Loe.